  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Border Town was once a peaceful and tranquil paradise, but it has become a ruin due to the full-scale invasion of orcs. The villagers scattered in fear, leaving only an old man who remained, harboring hopes of rebuilding the village. One day, you unexpectedly faint in the forest by the town, thus beginning an adventure intertwined with the fate of it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/7b577fd6ac47d7173d8af7092f7dfc4f.avif?t=1757647077\" width=600 height=155 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/23d2e18633a151cdb398467b4a5dc794.poster.avif?t=1757647077\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/23d2e18633a151cdb398467b4a5dc794.webm?t=1757647077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/23d2e18633a151cdb398467b4a5dc794.mp4?t=1757647077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore this world without restraint. Cross through different scenes such as jungles, wetlands, snowfields, and deserts, overcoming the unknown challenges brought by the alternation of day and night and the dark environments underground. Face threats from various fantastical creatures, encounter NPCs with different personalities, and experience one extraordinary story after another.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/6e44331ad70b057e756bebabc9f8167c.poster.avif?t=1757647077\" width=602 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/6e44331ad70b057e756bebabc9f8167c.webm?t=1757647077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/6e44331ad70b057e756bebabc9f8167c.mp4?t=1757647077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/c1be340e672e116f09ae33251e4f3af3.avif?t=1757647077\" width=600 height=155 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/7c6fb789f6d1f6330f5cf6dea9a0b526.poster.avif?t=1757647077\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/7c6fb789f6d1f6330f5cf6dea9a0b526.webm?t=1757647077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/7c6fb789f6d1f6330f5cf6dea9a0b526.mp4?t=1757647077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After communicating with the villagers and building relationships, you can recruit them to join the team for the town’s reconstruction. Each villager has a unique profession, ranging from farmers to miners, lumberjacks, and even bunny girls. And they will become important helpers in your efforts to build the town.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/46bcdac0d0439653d820bef9a90e2f54.avif?t=1757647077\" width=600 height=155 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/78a2c7b00d7c71fb7ec99da9e0eccf3a.poster.avif?t=1757647077\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/78a2c7b00d7c71fb7ec99da9e0eccf3a.webm?t=1757647077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/78a2c7b00d7c71fb7ec99da9e0eccf3a.mp4?t=1757647077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can choose to explore and play in this world freely in their preferred way, whether it’s cultivating farmland, raising animals, chopping trees, mining, gathering resources, building houses, or even accepting guild commissions to hunt monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/a68ecb580dcb1856db303b0811c0dd06.avif?t=1757647077\" width=600 height=155 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/195c0b4a11d00bd838a837b6e8a9b225.poster.avif?t=1757647077\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/195c0b4a11d00bd838a837b6e8a9b225.webm?t=1757647077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/195c0b4a11d00bd838a837b6e8a9b225.mp4?t=1757647077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features over 600 unique items, including various crops, equipment, tools, weapons, gears, and materials. Players can plant a vast array of crops and cook them into various delicacies, or create workbenches, build houses, equipping themselves with more powerful weapons to face the impending enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/8b9694ecd3c4ccc2081a917d32037280.avif?t=1757647077\" width=600 height=155 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/84b0ca9e2f988bb47f4e49989cc4c2c0.poster.avif?t=1757647077\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/84b0ca9e2f988bb47f4e49989cc4c2c0.webm?t=1757647077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/84b0ca9e2f988bb47f4e49989cc4c2c0.mp4?t=1757647077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While managing the village, don’t forget your primary duty as an adventurer! Head to the adventure guild to take on quests, prepare supplies, and traverse forests, snowfields, and deserts to eliminate monsters. Explore abandoned camps to find treasures, restore them as strongholds, and defeat goblin enemies, snowmen, and stonemen guarding the minerals. Purchase treasure maps to unlock clues, dig for hidden precious treasures around the world, and let the world know your adventure legend!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Border Town was once a peaceful and tranquil paradise, but it has become a ruin due to the full-scale invasion of orcs. The villagers scattered in fear, leaving only an old man who remained, harboring hopes of rebuilding the village. One day, you unexpectedly faint in the forest by the town, thus beginning an adventure intertwined with the fate of it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/7b577fd6ac47d7173d8af7092f7dfc4f.avif?t=1757647077\" width=600 height=155 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/23d2e18633a151cdb398467b4a5dc794.poster.avif?t=1757647077\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/23d2e18633a151cdb398467b4a5dc794.webm?t=1757647077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/extras/23d2e18633a151cdb398467b4a5dc794.mp4?t=1757647077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore this world without restraint. Cross through different scenes such as jungles, wetlands, snowfields, and deserts, overcoming the unknown challenges brought by the alternation of day and night and the dark environments underground. Face threats from various fantastical creatures, encounter NPCs with different personalities, and experience one extraordinary story after another.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1967820/